{"tid":1948631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃色 Patreon 圈整合","createTime":"2020-03-29T06:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T15:54:55.000Z","uid":26836,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"50ab8353e44141413eb6f43ed7065d5a20938ee8","tid":1948631,"uid":26836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T06:47:41.000Z","msg":"好多黃色content creator 其實一直都好需要大家支持<br />\n<br />\n一直都好想整合一個 <span style=\"color: gold;\">黃色</span> <span style=\"color: violet;\">Patreon</span> 圈 嘅list<br />\n簡單講 <span style=\"color: violet;\">Patreon</span> 就係一個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">課金平台</span></span>，課唔同金額就會有唔同level 嘅membership<br />\n每個creator都可以自己定收幾多錢，咩level 嘅membership 可以睇到啲咩post<br />\n<br />\n可能你會問我youtube 都可以刷view 數支持啦 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">點解要用 Patreon？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">原因有二</span><br />\n一、<br />\n好多content creator 以 YouTuber 嘅形式去推廣自己嘅創作 <br />\n不過大家知道YouTube  <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">黃標問題嚴重</span></span> 就算條片有好多view 數 <br />\n收入都未必夠佢地自給自足，更唔好講要再create 更多更好嘅content 俾大家<br />\n<br />\n二、<br />\n有啲人嘅創作形式其實而家好少平台可以俾佢地賺到錢<br />\n例如音樂創作，好多時啲streaming service <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">食水勁深</span></span>，<br />\n你播一次，個作者可能只會拎到$0.01<br />\n仲慘過5毛<br />\n<br />\n而 Patreon 就算係一個暫時嚟講唔錯 ，又多人用嘅平台<br />\n可以cater 到唔同創作形式嘅 creator<br />\n抽佣 聽返嚟好似比 YouTube 少<br />\n咁當然你直接過數就仲直接添<br />\n(歡迎指正)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">以下係我抛吓磚，大家有補充可以隨便comment</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 蕭若元說</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://patreon.com/mrshiu?utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_campaign=creatorshare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpatreon.com%2Fmrshiu%3Futm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dtwitter%26utm_campaign%3Dcreatorshare&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJe%2BIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=dd551ef9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://patreon.com/mrshiu?utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_campaign=creatorshare</a><br />\n<br />\n唔洗我講啦 燒山好嘢<br />\n不過佢已經有萬幾patrons follow，單單係呢個平台月入已經十幾萬<br />\n唔係太有能力嘅可以優先支持其他人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2.  DGXMUSIC</span> </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://patreon.com/dgxmusic?utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_campaign=creatorshare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpatreon.com%2Fdgxmusic%3Futm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dtwitter%26utm_campaign%3Dcreatorshare&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJe%2BIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=2d43af39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://patreon.com/dgxmusic?utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_campaign=creatorshare</a><br />\n<br />\n係手足嘅都唱過 <span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">願榮光</span></span> 啦，人地咁辛苦作首歌課少少金都無所謂啦<br />\n創作團隊仲出過fb post 叫大家支持<br />\n識做啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3. JASON的遊戲頻道 HunggyGames</span> </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://patreon.com/hunggy?utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_campaign=creatorshare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpatreon.com%2Fhunggy%3Futm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dtwitter%26utm_campaign%3Dcreatorshare&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJe%2BIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=6fc549ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://patreon.com/hunggy?utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_campaign=creatorshare</a><br />\n<br />\n其實即係大J<br />\n今日唔係要鬥黃，所以唔好同我話佢唔夠黃etc啦 <br />\n覺得佢值得支持 就課 唔值就唔課<br />\n就係咁簡單<br />\n<br />\n我暫時個list 係得3個，<br />\n大家有更多值得支持嘅請盡情comment"},{"pid":"f3479efa5e4f0b9f6918661d37e2fafe65c9ac8b","tid":1948631,"uid":125168,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T06:48:14.000Z","msg":"留名等睇電子雞list"},{"pid":"8bfd54227b409904a132adea653b6777f0f42